{
  "id": "adv_main_03_11_05",
  "title": "BIG4編1章55話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……これが、mihoさんから聞いた話の顛末です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That’s the gist of what I heard from Miho-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんにそんな過去が……\nありがとう、琴乃。お疲れ様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "DoriKyun had a past like that…\nThanks‚ Kotono. Good work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "……苛烈ですね。私達が同じ立場になったとしても\n彼女達ほど強くいられるでしょうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That’s harsh. Even if we were in the same position‚\ncould we be as strong as they are…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんはこの話を聞いて、どう思ったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What did you think after hearing this story‚ Kotono-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6962354501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "れもんさんと来夢さんの過去は\n理解出来るところも、同情出来るところもあった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were parts of Lemon-san and Laim-san’s past\nthat I could understand‚ and parts that I could sympathize with.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "不正に手を染める大人、本気じゃないアイドル\nそれに、アイドルを守るどころか切り捨てる事務所",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Adults who engage in fraud‚ idols who aren’t serious‚\nand agencies that abandon idols instead of protecting them‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "落ち目になった途端、態度を変える周りの人達――\n何もかも嫌いになって、復讐してやりたいって想いも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "people around them who change their attitude the moment they fall from grace――\nI get the feeling of wanting to hate everything and get revenge…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.299999237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "そんな世界を変えたいっていう想いも\n……分かる気がする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…and I think I understand the feeling of wanting to change that world.\nI get it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.4333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2886603991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、それは月ストが目指すべき姿じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that’s not the way Moon Tempest should be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.862468918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 62.3666610717
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "私達月のテンペストは、五人だけじゃない\n一緒に高みを目指す、星見プロの仲間がいる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We‚ Moon Tempest‚ aren’t just five people.\nWe have our Hoshimi Productions comrades who are aiming for the top with us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2666623432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "それに、三枝さんやさとみさん\n――{user}さんがいてくれる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ there’s Saegusa-san‚ Satomi-san‚\n――and Manager-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.266669464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3822103101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "だから、もしれもんさんと来夢さんと同じような境遇に\n陥っても、私達はどりきゅんのようにはならない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So even if we fall into the same situation as Lemon-san and Laim-san‚\nwe won’t become like DoriKyun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.9333473203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……それじゃあ、どりきゅんの過去を知ったことは\n無駄だったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So knowing about DoriKyun’s past…\n…was a waste?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0666753131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ、無駄じゃありません\n二人の過去を知って、改めて思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it wasn’t a waste.\nAfter learning about their past‚ I thought about it again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.0000124611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "私は……相手と正面から向き合って\n気持ちを知って、気持ちを通い合わせて戦いたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I…want to face my opponent head-on‚\nunderstand their feelings‚ and fight them after our feelings connect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.3666791277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "そして――観に来てくれた人達に\n最高のライブバトルを届けたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And――\n…I want to deliver the best live battle to the people who came to see us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7000124611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、やっぱり琴乃ちゃんはそうでなくちゃ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that’s our Kotono-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.1280397174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "まったくですわ。闇落ちなんて琴乃には似合い\nませんわよ？　慣れないことをするものではありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Absolutely. Falling into darkness doesn’t suit\nyou at all‚ Kotono. You shouldn't try things you’re not used to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.9317248835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "や、闇落ち！？\nそんなことしたつもりは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "F-Falling into darkness!?\nI wasn’t…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.1000124611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁまぁ\nそれより、琴乃ちゃん。……決めたんだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ now.\nMore importantly‚ Kotono-chan…you’ve decided‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.3025976656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 140.1000124611
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "うん\n{user}さん、改めてお願いがあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah.\nManager-san‚ I have a request.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.1000124611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "月のテンペストと、どりきゅんのライブバトルを\nもう一度、やらせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please let Moon Tempest\nhave another live battle with DoriKyun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.100529395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃の気持ちも、みんなの気持ちもよく分かった\nでも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand Kotono’s feelings‚ and everyone else’s feelings.\nBut…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.7017666465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "今すぐにという訳じゃありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It doesn’t have to be right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.0682587699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと前から……I-UNITYの頃から\n考えていることがあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve had something on my mind\nfor a long time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.1333447771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "それって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could that be…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.4101379629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_05-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "『アイドルとは何か』の答えを見つけたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to find the answer to “what is an idol?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.1584599331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 172.9666781105
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_flashback-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 173.2056707218
    },
    {
